invalid type: string "Karnataka Idea2PoC Grant Purpose: Support early-stage startups with funding to validate concepts (Proof of Concept). Eligibility: Early-stage startups in Karnataka; specific tracks for women (Elevate Women) and SC/ST founders (Elevate Unnati). Benefits: Grant-in-aid of ₹10–50 lakh for prototype/PoC stage. Application: Online via Startup Karnataka portal during open calls.